{"tid":1638204,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"重講《五大訴求》根本係冇腦","createTime":"2019-10-08T08:41:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T09:45:13.000Z","uid":331469,"like":8,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"7f441b4697d7a04a0b2f96fb01709336380cc4b6","tid":1638204,"uid":331469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T08:41:55.000Z","msg":"首先我要屌曬你地<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"> 如果有五大訴求你地就收貨，咁你地日日嗌 ｛解散警隊，刻不容緩｝黎做咩9?</span> <br />\n<br />\n唔好再屌咩六大訴求會比人覺得得寸進尺<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你覺得宜家就要求六大訴求   定  如果到時政府答應五大訴求，我地先再話要加多個訴求：解散警隊   邊個情況會顯得寸進尺d?</span></span><br />\n<br />\n其實好多心水清既手足都知獨立調查委員會一定唔夠/冇撚用，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"> 如果到時先轉呔，國際一定會反彈，就會比國際，藍絲話我地得寸進尺，到時港共必定會食住上</span><br />\n<br />\n所以唔好再屌9六大訴求，因為<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">訴求係跟比例!!</span></span> 對比提出《五大訴求》時既7月同 宜家既10月，無論係警暴，濫權，港共打壓既程度根本係小巫見大巫，<span style=\"color: red;\">所以我地既訴求係絕對要同警察濫權/港共打壓程度跟比例升級</span>，文宣亦要捉住呢解釋。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">點解獨立調查委員已經唔夠?</span></span><br />\n因為事已至此，警暴日日超越你想像<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">問下你自己 假設政府真係跪低，答應五大訴求，成立獨立調查委員會，調查警隊，你會就咁接受咩???</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">上網睇下以往幾次獨立調查 e.g南丫島事故，最後係有邊次係有人要負責???<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n我當就你個獨立調查真係會有成效，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但今次運動係香港史無前例，警方濫權持續數個月，調查順要幾多時間?<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">一年，兩年?三年?宜家講緊係調查成個警隊呀!!</span></span></span><br />\n<br />\n就算調查完，<span style=\"font-size: large;\">你覺得會有幾多人要負責?幾千人係絕對冇可能!!!但問題係宜家3萬人既警隊有大部份人都犯緊法!!</span><br />\n<br />\n無錯最後相信最多只會有數百個指揮官，中高層，網上比人斷正濫權既速龍，防暴，散仔會比人攞出黎祭旗。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">所以唯一辦法：解散警隊  係一定要!!</span> 雖然係冇可能，<span style=\"color: red;\">但呢個訴求強硬既程度遠大於 獨立委員會，如果政府要跪低，想同我地談判，我地都可以就呢個咁強硬既訴求 要求 一定數量既警察付上刑責</span>(起碼都要求 解散成個速龍，防暴，一千人以上)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以宜家立即加上解散警察，唔好再屌<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">六大訴求，缺一不可!</span></span>"},{"pid":"0e9f3374ddfc4f797ae51ba5fd18b8bd992a2b23","tid":1638204,"uid":331469,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T08:42:47.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"9eab941ec69ac2b04d0ff7271e8520dbf3b2baba","tid":1638204,"uid":331469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T08:43:05.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"507e242097425796fa53c45e2b2208fe8199c5dd","tid":1638204,"uid":188176,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T08:44:17.000Z","msg":"想引人重覆十點鐘鳩嗌變九點既失敗<br />\n而家共產黨真係好驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06f21e0be2fd17003db5e35bbffebab44ce20c47","tid":1638204,"uid":331469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T08:58:49.000Z","msg":"咁我問你 到時有5大訴求 你要就咁收貨 即刻唔上街??"},{"pid":"e1c121d22efbc833c70366e7b6e9b0447366e8a0","tid":1638204,"uid":331469,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"507e242097425796fa53c45e2b2208fe8199c5dd","tid":1638204,"uid":188176,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T08:44:17.000Z","msg":"想引人重覆十點鐘鳩嗌變九點既失敗<br />\n而家共產黨真係好驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T08:59:05.000Z","msg":"咁我問你 到時有5大訴求 你要就咁收貨 即刻唔上街??"},{"pid":"e4170fefe21ba23ead66c280e7d6d750173ed947","tid":1638204,"uid":331469,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"507e242097425796fa53c45e2b2208fe8199c5dd","tid":1638204,"uid":188176,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T08:44:17.000Z","msg":"想引人重覆十點鐘鳩嗌變九點既失敗<br />\n而家共產黨真係好驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T09:00:15.000Z","msg":"連登大台就係咁 唔岩意見就比人屌5毛"},{"pid":"946a146681f82a79576159a4d643c9d37f7a788c","tid":1638204,"uid":331469,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T09:03:12.000Z","msg":"你地全部人唔好再嗌 <span style=\"color: red;\">解散警隊 刻不容緩</span>呀竹，反正有5大訴求 你地就會收貨，解唔解散都唔緊要啦，求其嗌下姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3178b4b07edba0903862ec2f293fd506c0148146","tid":1638204,"uid":331469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T09:07:45.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"09a72bdf0d42956b4ee9315e4e8056a700215c19","tid":1638204,"uid":331469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T09:07:58.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"2e8e3e3b250c8a3e71c85d13ecdb3f8478a284d5","tid":1638204,"uid":331469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T09:10:59.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"27f245329b484f35f4e8aa4fdc4781bec6e4eace","tid":1638204,"uid":331469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T09:17:17.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"31ad39ce6586588fe769661d32c975ebff01789e","tid":1638204,"uid":331469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T09:22:32.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"5cdf2d07ccb1aaa8153764ff8fe5329bfdd9ee42","tid":1638204,"uid":105691,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T09:24:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢搞店左五大訴求你估解散警隊有冇份"},{"pid":"28a04dd46df00c2837637da1efad804d5cd27ede","tid":1638204,"uid":105691,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T09:25:59.000Z","msg":"分化撚確定"},{"pid":"24fe4c42316d17776d6ba242b1c5ec77bd601413","tid":1638204,"uid":55955,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T09:26:41.000Z","msg":"有普選的話，你講多廿個訴求都得<br />\n到時列個表出嚟，邊個候選人應承最多訴求，香港人就投邊個<br />\n<br />\n爭論五大定六大訴求根本就係弱智<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />瞓醒未"},{"pid":"273262f3ff11550c1ef0dac14cf6a637c8a27650","tid":1638204,"uid":64689,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":